      (MHLW) to extend the indication for Soliris® (eculizumab) 
      as a potential treatment for patients with refractory generalized 
      myasthenia gravis (gMG) who are anti-acetylcholine receptor (AChR) 
      antibody-positive. The submission is supported by comprehensive data 
      from the Phase 3 REGAIN study.
    
    
