      researchers presented new data from an analysis of patients enrolled in 
      the Global atypical Hemolytic Uremic Syndrome (aHUS) Registry, 
      demonstrating that initiation of Soliris® (eculizumab) prior 
      to kidney transplant reduces the risk of dialysis post-transplant in 
      patients with aHUS. Specifically, results showed that starting Soliris 
      prior to transplant reduced the likelihood ofmore...
